snippet.title: Battle Chess Special Edition gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Battle Chess Special Edition, PC game produced by Interplay in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/battle-chess-special-edition/14082/
Battle Chess Special Edition is a bundle, it contains three interesting games  of chess. Has a fantastic graphics and the pieces were holograms that fought together when a piece was taken.
Played through modern Windows machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Battle Chess (MPC version) - https://youtu.be/V1H7FYvfLy8
Battle Chess - https://youtu.be/v46h3jqf0Nw
Battle Chess 4000 - https://youtu.be/3NeSNDb8ieM
